rets to discover<br><br>Fast-paced, bullet-hell bosses<br><br>4 difficulties for hardcores and amateurs alike<br><br>Bonus challenge rooms<br><br>Traditional hand-drawn character art and illustrations in dialogue scenes.<br><br>Cute chibi girls                                                                                                          <br><br>Changeable outfits<br><br>Post game content<br><br>EPILEPSY WARNING - This game contains many flashing images. Play at your own risk    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/3907a407b65722ad3abaeaa61a8b78a2.apng?t=1731442594\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/3907a407b65722ad3abaeaa61a8b78a2.poster.avif?t=1731442594\" class=\"bb_img\" width=17 height=17 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/d3619625d109f6a5c841bbe075395e3a.poster.avif?t=1731442594\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/d3619625d109f6a5c841bbe075395e3a.webm?t=1731442594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/411edeae409caf50e147ef7bebce5b1b.webp?t=1731442594\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281070/extras/411edeae409caf50e147ef7bebce5b1b.poster.avif?t=1731442594\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span>",
